items.sentence: I thought that you didn't want us to call Tom.
I thought that you said that no one liked Tom.
I thought that I'd be able to do that for Tom.
Tom knows that I can't speak French very well.
Tom said that Mary is good at speaking French.
I remember the first time that I ever saw Tom.
I suspect Tom and Mary have gone to Australia.
I wish we could go to Australia and visit Tom.
You can't imagine how difficult it is for Tom.
I think both Tom and Mary were born in Boston.
